title: Jolly Reindeers 4 - Punk, Love N Christmas
description:
picture it. fourth album, four members, the saga continues...
out of a dark rift in time and space emerges something so volatile, and sassy, it will cause the grown man to weep as he experiences the ultimate in christmas rock n' roll terror.
yes, we speak of the unstoppable force of th jolly reindeers 4.
birthed out of a desire to recreate, redefine and release the world's most dangerous christmas songs. you now have the power to unleash this potent WMD. use it for good...not evil.
first and foremost we would like to thank santa. firstly, for conquering the martians. secondly, for breaking all known laws of physics. lastly, for conquering the martians.
